        <tag-mode>multi</tag-mode>
        <tag-value>The background of Swergies rikes lag 1734.
                    The background is made of old brown leather and when dragging a finger across the surface of the back it is 
                    generally a smooth texture, interrupted only by the occasional scratch and dry patch.
                    In contrast the spine of the book is rough and severly dried out. When handling the artefact, our cotton gloves
                    frequently snagged on its imperfect surface.
                    Taken with the iteration 3 setup. 
        </tag-value>
